snippet.title: Bubble Spinner Gameplay
snippet.description:
SUBSCRIBE
Bubble Spinner
Author:DeadWhale
Description:Pop bubbles? Yeah, I know how to do that. But the whole glob moves every time I hit it! Oh noes! You'll have to use strategic thinking, bud.
Category:Puzzle and Board
PLAY AT: http://www.addictinggames.com/bubblespinner.html
